{{/NODE_PROJECT}}

## Session Lifecycle

### On Session Start (READ)

1. Read this file
2. Read {{DEPTH_FILE}} for current state
3. Check `memory/MEMORY.md` for persistent context
4. Check if retro is due (see `memory/retro.md`)

### On Session End (UPDATE)

1. Update {{DEPTH_FILE}} if state changed
2. Add changelog entry if work was done
3. Update `memory/` if new learnings
4. Increment task count in `memory/retro.md`

